Cyber Claw:






The creature had finally let go of Cyber Claw, and as it did so, she dropped 
to the ground. She activated her thrustors to slow her fall. She landed in a 
crouched position. Pain was almost all over her body. But she didn't worry 
about it too much. She had had more damage than this. Once the top side of 
her head was blown off. But she was able to get the repairs she needed. 
Here, she was alone.

She stumbled forwards, then turned to the giant beast struggling with the 
other raptor.

"He will never find me!" she called to it, still thinking it was sent by 
Megatron to track her. "Tell him he will never find me!"

She bolted away from the two dinosaurs, and mumbled, "Flight mode." Her huge 
body lifted into the air, and accended to the forest. She flew over it, and 
drived into the canopy in the distance.
